sections.heading: is amended by Enrolled
sections.text:
House Bill 3991 (2025 special session). As of the date of publication of the

2025 Edition of the Oregon Revised Statutes, Enrolled House Bill 3991 (2025

special session) is subject to potential referendum petitions that may be filed

with the Secretary of State as provided in Article IV, section 1, of the Oregon

Constitution. The full text of Enrolled House Bill 3991 (2025 special session)

is set forth following 801.610.
